reviewText: Stop wondering if you should get this or not. The wrestling showcased on this dvd is great and has plenty of matches for alll of the superstars.

This has a TON of classic wrestling, it looks to be from the late 1980's when people knew how to wrestle plus the audience is enjoying themselves unlike these days when people just sit there quietly and clap once in a while.
Before anyone spends any money on this dvd,we really need more info from Amazon.com as to whether this is a dvd full of interviews or matches and if it has matches why are they not listed.
